title: Fight Class 3 (Webtoon Version)
description:
Description :
        A world in which Korea is the global capital of combat sports. At Nam-Il High School where the best and most talented students of martial arts reside, Jiu Ji-Tae suddenly finds himself thrust into their midst despite being a total weakling.   By neutralizing his physical shortcomings through jiu-jitsu, can he rise to the top of the fight classes?  ---**Links:**  - (https://twitter.com/mymmx89)
